text: "Lonely Boy" is a 2011 song by The Black Keys and is the leading single from their seventh studio album El Camino. It is one of their most successful songs from the band and went to number 64 in the United States, number 80 in the United Kingdom and the Netherlands and number 33 in Canada. It won 2 Grammy Awards in 2013. ==Track listing== ==Notes== ==References== Category:2011 songs Category:Garage rock songs Category:Blues rock songs Category:The Black Keys songs
